    // ═══ CREATURE-COMBAT-OVERHAUL §2e VARIANT LADDERS (2026-07-11) ═══════════════════════════
    // 5-tier × 3-variant ladders for wolf/bear/boar/goblin/orc/thornwood_spider. Every entry rolls
