    // ── KINGDOMS-TRADE visiting parties ─────────────────────────────────────
    // Kingdom folk arrive only as spawned parties (KingdomService) — empty biomeWeights keeps them
    // out of the ambient spawner. entityClass "animal" + neutral/passive so nothing auto-engages;
    // they carry `kingdomId`/`partyId` on the Mob, and harming them sours kingdom relations.
    // Caravan/visitor humanoids render as PEOPLE: the `map` sheet's humanoid sprites (the same set
    // colonists draw from), retinted per role via fg. The pack beast keeps its aurochs glyph.
